WEBVTT

00:00:00.877 --> 00:00:04.120
Kao znanstvenica, ali i kao ljudsko biće

00:00:04.120 --> 00:00:06.124
pokušavam se podložiti

00:00:06.124 --> 00:00:09.499
divljenju.

00:00:09.499 --> 00:00:12.368
Mislim da je Jason Webley to sinoć nazvao

00:00:12.368 --> 00:00:16.395
"zavjerom bivanja dijelom čarolije".

00:00:16.395 --> 00:00:19.216
Stoga, sva sreća da mi karijera biologa

00:00:19.216 --> 00:00:21.860
dozvoljava dublje uronjavanje u živote

00:00:21.860 --> 00:00:24.378
nekih zbilja divnih stvorenja

00:00:24.378 --> 00:00:26.757
na našoj planeti:

00:00:26.757 --> 00:00:28.452
krijesnica.

00:00:28.452 --> 00:00:30.735
Sada, znam da za mnoge od vas krijesnice